{"tid":1172811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：政府可保障市民受公平審訊","createTime":"2019-05-26T16:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T17:06:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c2eacd6378f97322217ec5f1cdbeb1883b7485d0","tid":1172811,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1459426_1_L_20190526162637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1459426_1_L_20190526162637.jpg&h=47a2287f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗撰寫網誌指向外國商會講解逃犯條例修例後，部分明確認同及支持修例，他之後出席公開活動時透露是亞洲的商會，又指大部分的亞洲國家及部分歐洲國家都沒有問題，只是部分有既定立場。<br />\n<br />\n歐美等國家先後質疑逃犯條例修例，政務司司長張建宗在網誌表示，上周向外國商會講解部分與會者了解實情後，認為能夠彰顯法治，明確表示認同和支持修例。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗之後出席公開活動被追問下透露，支持修例的是一個亞洲商會。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗重申香港司法獨立全球排名第八，法庭可以把關，而疑犯移交前行政長官亦可加設要求，確保公平審訊。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指條例複雜，市民不理解屬合理，政府會加強解說並繼續與不同界別團體磋商，澄清誤解及消除不必要的恐懼。"},{"pid":"4c0c9824703a3fc391875d31fbbfa4c1d0b5cc96","tid":1172811,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=349381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349381&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=10833306\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349381&h=834c12c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=349381</a>"},{"pid":"0987e0c5546ea8d6b7ec7faa685ac17b7fa56304","tid":1172811,"uid":193642,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"政府呃鬼食豆腐依招用左咁多年, 全世界都知下屆政府有政治需要就會搬出黎用, 以為咁樣仲可以呃到人"},{"pid":"8e4c498eab6466fb99b441363bf5e96e514a6b43","tid":1172811,"uid":25900,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"repl